Create the game [Game]
    Create a blank 3x3 grid as game board [Board]
    Create two players [Player]
    Select choice of symbol [Player]
    Determine who goes first [Game]

Start the loop to alternate turns [Game]
    Display the board [Board]
    Collect players valid move [Player]
    If win or tie conditions are present [Game]
        Display message for win or tie, ask for rematch
        If new game is selected [Player]
            Create new game [Game]
            Exit loop
    Else
        Continue to the next turn/loop [Game]
